BEGIN_PGML

It's given that [` 1 \text{ meter} = 1000 \text{ millimeters} `]. Do the following unit conversions.

a. [`` [$m1] \text{ meters} = ``] [__________]{$mm1} [`` \text{ millimeters} ``]

a. [`` [$mm2] \text{ millimeters} = ``] [__________]{$m2} [`` \text{ meters} ``]

